title: VonZipper : Donavon Frankenreiter in the Hoss
description: Become the H.I.M.C... Deposit the Hoss on your mug and command respect from your new found subordinates. Work more efficiently and take longer lunch breaks, who says you have to pay the cost to be the boss...
